## Usage

To use this software, either copy the program(s) in the bin directory
to a directory mentioned in your PATH environment variable or add the
directory to the PATH environment variable.

See the web page https://github.com/melsman/apltail for general
information about the usage of the system. The lib/ directory contains
the prelude.apl file and the tests/ directory contains APL test files.

## Running the tests

To run the tests in the test/ directory, execute the following
commands:

   $ cd tests/
   $ APLT=../bin/aplt PRELUDE=../lib/prelude.apl make test

